headline: Stephens & Co. Maintains Equal-Weight on Hormel Foods, Lowers Price Target to $25
summary: Stephens & Co.  analyst Pooran Sharma   maintains Hormel Foods (NYSE:HRL) with a Equal-Weight and lowers the price target from $27 to $25.
